Lisa HATTRICH and John Hattrich, Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
Clyde NEIL and County of Ocean, Defendants,
and
State of New Jersey, Defendant-Respondent. C-765 September Term 2018
082360 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002716-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
